This project is a simple push mode publisher for esgf data-nodes.
----------------------
Command Line Arguments
----------------------

Example:  esgpost --schema cmip5 --master_id testId --instance_id testId --file_type Dataset
          --dataset_id TestDatasetId --id TestId --version 1 --publish

--schema, --master_id, --instance_id, --file_type, --dataset_id, --id, --version :
    (required) Specifies mandatory metadata that cannot be harvested directly from netCDF files.

--publish / --unpublish :
    (required) Specifies the type of action the user wishes to accomplish.
    PS: In the case of unpublish --mapfile is used to specify the path of the mapfile describing
    the data to be unpublished.
